info.name: Momio Beige Aesthetic Theme
info.description: Welcome to my brand new Momio theme! With this theme, your Momio will become a beige dream with a beautiful interface! I hope you like this new theme for Momio. It's the very first version and I will update this theme and make improvements! Thanks for using it.
